These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-5-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, argentine, polish, indonesian
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, dog, hedgehog, horse
4 different games are played: bridge, mah-jongg, go, poker
1. the person playing poker is between the owner of the rabbit and the argentine##2
2. the person playing poker is in an odd position##4
3. the malaysian is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
4. the person playing bridge is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
5. the indonesian is somewhere to the right of the person playing mah-jongg##5
6. the person playing go is somewhere to the right of the argentine##5
7. the owner of the hedgehog is the person playing poker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |      3      |    4    |
| Nationality         | polish | argentine   | malaysian     | indonesian |
| Pet   | horse   | dog | hedgehog | rabbit  |
| Game   | bridge        | mah-jongg     | poker         | go     |

