.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-5-2::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, epic, action, scientific
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, vegafina, old-henry, swisher
4 different pets are kept: snake, guinea-pig, goat, turtle
1. the owner of the goat is the swisher-smoker##1
2. the person watching action movies is between the owner of the guinea-pig and the owner of the goat##2
3. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the vegafina-smoker##3
4. the owner of the goat is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1
5. the old-henry-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person watching epic movies##5
6. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
7. the person watching epic movies is somewhere to the left of the old-henry-smoker##5
8. the prince-smoker is the person watching family movies##1
9. the owner of the snake is on the left of the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre      | family      | epic | action  | scientific    |
| Cigar           | prince | swisher     | old-henry | vegafina  |
| Pet   | snake | goat    | turtle | guinea-pig |

