.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-5-3::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, biathlon, volleyball, tennis
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: superhero, fantasy, crime, epic
City: edinburgh, nizza, prague, berlin
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
2. the person watching superhero movies is between the person watching epic movies and the person watching crime movies##2
3. the person who's sport is sailing is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to berlin##5
4. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1
5. the person traveling to prague is somewhere to the left of the person watching fantasy movies##5
6. the person traveling to berlin is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##5
7. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
8. the person who's sport is volleyball is somewhere to the right of the person watching crime movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |     3      |     4     |
| Sport         | sailing   | tennis | volleyball | biathlon   |
| Movie-Genre           | crime | superhero  | epic      | fantasy |
| City   | prague        | berlin  | edinburgh      | nizza   |

