.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-5-4::.
4 different pets are kept: lizard, ferret, goat, hamster
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, lacrosse, snowboarding, rugby
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: aconite, sunflower, begonia, rose
1. the person who growsrose is somewhere to the right of the owner of the ferret##5
2. the person who growsaconite is somewhere to the left of the person who growsbegonia##5
3. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the person who growsrose##3
4. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is somewhere to the left of the owner of the lizard##5
6. the person who growsbegonia is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is rugby##5
7. the person who growsbegonia is in an even position##4
8. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3
9. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |   3    |      4      |
| Pet           | goat     | ferret | hamster | lizard |
| Sport   | snowboarding      | lacrosse     | rugby   | cycling   |
| Flower   | aconite | begonia    | rose | sunflower     |

