.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-5-5::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: water-polo, badminton, rowing, ice-hockey
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, vegafina, montecristo, bongani
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, milk, tea, fanta
1. the person drinking milk is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1
2. the person who's sport is water-polo is somewhere to the left of the montecristo-smoker##5
3. the vegafina-smoker is on the far right##1
4. the person who's sport is rowing is the vegafina-smoker##1
5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
6. the person drinking water is the swisher-smoker##1
7. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is somewhere to the right of the person drinking water##5
8. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |      3       |    4     |
| Sport           | badminton | water-polo       | ice-hockey | rowing |
| Cigar   | swisher    | bongani | montecristo      | vegafina     |
| Beverage   | water      | milk     | tea       | fanta     |

