.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-5-6::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, jet-ski, subway, helicopter
There are 4 different favourite colors: ivory, turquise, orange, aquamarine
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, country, d&b, soul
 1. the person who likes aquamarine is between the person who likes ivory and the fan of soul##2
 2. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
 3. the person who likes turquise is somewhere to the right of the fan of soul##5
 4. the person who likes ivory is on the left or right of the person who likes aquamarine##3
 5. the person who likes ivory is somewhere to the right of the fan of country##5
 6. the fan of hip-hop is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3
 7. the fan of country is somewhere to the left of the person driving the jet-ski##5
 8. the person driving the subway is somewhere to the left of the person who likes aquamarine##5
 9. the person who likes ivory is somewhere to the right of the person driving the subway##5
10. the person driving the jet-ski is somewhere to the right of the person who likes ivory##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3      |     4      |
| Transport   | subway    | helicopter | train      | jet-ski |
| Color           | orange      | aquamarine   | ivory | turquise       |
| Music-Genre         | soul | country | hip-hop   | d&b   |

