.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-5-7::.
There 4 different types of food: corn, papaya, plum, avocado
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigold, daffodil, tulip, dahlia
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, manager, security-guard, librarian
1. the security-guard is on the left or right of the analyst##3
2. the person who growstulip is between the person eating avocado and the person eating papaya##2
3. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the librarian##1
4. the person eating papaya is on the right of the person eating plum##1
5. the person who growstulip is somewhere to the left of the security-guard##5
6. the person who growsdaffodil is somewhere to the left of the person who growsmarigold##5
7. the person eating avocado is the manager##1
8. the person eating corn is on the left or right of the person who growsdahlia##3
9. the person eating plum is on the left or right of the security-guard##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |    3    |     4     |
| Food      | avocado | plum | papaya   | corn       |
| Flower   | daffodil   | tulip       | dahlia | marigold |
| Job   | manager     | analyst       | security-guard    | librarian       |

