.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-5-8::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, dunhill, tiparillo, vegafina
4 different pets are kept: bird, chinchilla, horse, fish
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, collecting, drawing, card-games
1. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
2. the person who's hobby is drawing is the owner of the bird##1
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
4. the owner of the horse is somewhere to the right of the dunhill-smoker##5
5. the owner of the horse is on the left or right of the vegafina-smoker##3
6. the game-smoker is between the owner of the chinchilla and the person who's hobby is drawing##2
7. the person who's hobby is card-games is in an even position##4
8. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the owner of the chinchilla##1
9. the owner of the fish is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2    |     3      |       4       |
| Cigar    | dunhill       | game | vegafina   | tiparillo         |
| Pet         | bird     | horse  | chinchilla   | fish |
| Hobby   | drawing | card-games    | rock-climbing | collecting     |

