.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-5-9::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, zombie, epic, mystery
4 different pets are kept: turtle, pony, chinchilla, frog
There are 4 different favourite colors: red, white, yellow, coral
 1. the person who likes yellow is somewhere to the left of the owner of the chinchilla##5
 2. the owner of the turtle is the person who likes coral##1
 3. the person watching zombie movies is somewhere to the right of the person who likes yellow##5
 4. the person watching crime movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching epic movies##5
 5. the person watching zombie movies is in an odd position##4
 6. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
 7. the person who likes coral is somewhere to the right of the owner of the chinchilla##5
 8. the person who likes red is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the owner of the frog is in an even position##4
10. the person watching crime movies is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2    |       3        |      4       |
| Movie-Genre        | epic     | mystery | zombie     | crime    |
| Pet         | pony  | frog | chinchilla | turtle |
| Color   | red | yellow   | white        | coral   |

