3. the analyst is somewhere to the left of the librarian##5
4. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the engineer##1
5. the analyst is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
6. the chef is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
7. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
8. the analyst is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| City   | marseilles  | san-francisco     | venice    | liverpool |
| Beverage   | cola    | 7up      | coffee       | mirinda    |
| Job   | chef | engineer | analyst | librarian |

