2. the fan of disco is on the right of the fan of soul##1
3. the person driving the roller is the fan of disco##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the left of the person driving the trike##5
5. the person who growsdaisy is on the left or right of the person driving the motorbike##3
6. the person who growsmarigold is the person who growsmarigold##1
7. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the fan of soul##1
8. the person driving the subway is somewhere to the right of the fan of soul##5
9. the person who growsmarigold is somewhere to the right of the fan of disco##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |   2    |      3       |     4     |
| Transport         | motorbike       | trike  | roller | subway |
| Music-Genre   | indie | soul | disco     | dubstep     |
| Flower           | poppy   | daisy   | lily        | marigold    |

