3. the person who's hobby is traveling is between the person who's hobby is hiking and the person who growsbegonia##2
4. the person driving the trike is in an odd position##4
5. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the far left##1
6. the person who growslily is on the left or right of the person who growsballoon-flower##3
