.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-5-16::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, september, december, august
The people have 4 different jobs:  mechanic, paramedic, journalist, writer
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, skateboarding, cricket, badminton
 1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in january##3
 2. the writer is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in september##5
 3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the mechanic##1
 4. the mechanic is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
 5. the mechanic is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3
 7. the paramedic is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 8. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the mechanic##1
 9. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in december##3
10. the person who's sport is badminton is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in january##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Birthday          | august | december | january   | september       |
| Job   | paramedic | writer  | mechanic   | journalist |
| Sport     | cricket | badminton    | skateboarding | handball    |

