.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-5-20::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, comedy, western, thriller
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, singing, traveling, fishing
There are 4 different favourite colors: black, purple, apricot, red
1. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
2. the person watching thriller movies is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's hobby is fishing##2
3. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching comedy movies##5
4. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is reading##3
5. the person who likes red is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who likes red is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
7. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left or right of the person who likes black##3
8. the person who likes red is somewhere to the right of the person who likes black##5
9. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the person watching western movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy  | thriller  | horror | western |
| Hobby           | fishing     | singing | reading      | traveling    |
| Color     | purple | black      | apricot | red     |

 